message:
Custom questions have failed to load for a student. This means that a student is applying to an ATS linked job and is not fully seeing all the available custom questions. While they can still apply, they may have a partially filled out application. This can create inequity in the hiring process.
To rectify this, find the associated Bugsnag to determine the student and application affected. From there, work with a PM to help the student fill out the rest of the questions for the employer.

